  "description": "A stunning night view of a cityscape with prominent bridges and a vibrant fireworks display. The foreground features a modern, illuminated bridge stretching across dark water. Behind it, another older, ornate bridge is visible, also lit up. The city skyline is densely packed with buildings, their windows glowing with warm, yellow light. A spectacular fireworks explosion is positioned above the city, featuring bursts of red, white, and gold. The overall composition creates a sense of grandeur and celebration.",
